```plantuml
@startuml spagnuolocarmine_serverless-computing-for-iot

participant "IoT Device" as device
participant "RabbitMQ (AMQP/MQTT)" as broker
participant "Nuclio Producer Function" as producer
participant "Nuclio Consumer Function" as consumer
participant "Logger" as logger

device -> broker : Publishes temperature data (AMQP/MQTT)
broker -> producer : Triggers on message arrival
producer -> broker : Processes & forwards data
broker -> consumer : Delivers processed message
consumer -> logger : Sends data for logging
logger -> logger : Prints temperature to console

@enduml
```